    "headline": "Synchrony Financial (NYSE:SYF) Misses Q2 CY2026 Revenue Estimates",
    "summary": "Consumer financial services company Synchrony Financial (NYSE:SYF) fell short of the market’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2026, with sales falling 34.7% year on year to $2.38 billion. Its GAAP profit of $2.59 per share was 21.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
